name: Welcome To The Bowels Of Hell
description:
The Bowels Of Hell welcomes you!

Have you ever seen a perfectly mirrored MP4 NFT? You have now :-) This is not just an AI piece of art done with a couple of clicks (none of mine are tbh), this animation has been trimmed, cut, zoomed, sharpened in three different ways, resized, and also mirrored perfectly without a single sign that its not as it was when originally made.

Weeks of working this piece has left it to be what I believe is an NFT first! Welcome To The Bowels Of Hell is 1960 X 1120 in dimensions, 98.7MBs of A.I. animated MP4 art, and runs at 10 frames per second.
